snippet.title: Quicksand Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
"Quicksand" is our latest video game project, a thrilling third-person shooter that follows the story of an soldier in Middle East, who must navigate a dangerous world of terrorism, corruption, and mafia alliances in order to rescue his kidnapped family.

"Quicksand" is a third person shooter pc game. We are developing the game on Unreal Engine 5. Game is still in early development phase and we are planning to announce the release date this summer. 

Wishlist our game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2488490/QUICKSAND/

Don't forget to follow our social media accounts;
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@quicksandgame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GameQuicksand
Discord: https://discord.gg/gMGU5dXfPR

Video Edit: Mert Şişman
